    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts exactly as it should, making it a dependable choice for any driver. While the exterior shows some minor signs of normal use, such as light surface scratches and small stone chips on the hood, the paint still retains a great shine. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, with all electronic features and climate control systems functioning perfectly. It is a solid, reliable vehicle that is ready for its next owner.",
