    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained by its previous owner. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, providing a reliable driving experience. While the exterior paint retains a nice luster, you may find a few minor rock chips or light scratches consistent with regular use. The interior is clean and comfortable, with all major electronics and climate control systems functioning properly, though there is some very light wear on the driver's seat bolster. This is a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
