    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all project lovers and DIY enthusiasts! This car is ready for a total transformation and is the perfect candidate for someone looking to take on a rewarding restoration project. While it is currently in poor condition and will require substantial mechanical and cosmetic attention to return to its best, it serves as an affordable blank canvas for your automotive vision!",
