    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, maintained in impeccable showroom condition. This vehicle exhibits no discernible wear, reflecting a standard of meticulous care that preserves its original aesthetic and mechanical integrity. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, confirms its status as a premier acquisition for the discerning driver. We invite you to inspect this superior motorcar, which represents the pinnacle of its class.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
